text.tspan: The design for The Tanglenomicon project prioritizes flexibility and extensibility.
We want a feature, maybe "calculate Jones polynomial," to be runnable in a
jupyter notebook or on a university cluster. We're aiming for a "write once deploy
To that end weve decoupled functionality wherever feasible, taking a layered
The circle product combines a Montesinos tangle and a
rational tangle to create a generalized Montesinos tangle.
The circle product takes the NE, SE, SW strands of the
Montesinos tangle and alternates bottom and right twists as
described by the rational tangle's twist vector.
